// TextInput
// Single-line text input with label, validation, and controlled/uncontrolled support.

FUNCTION handleChange(e)
  Updates internal value state.
  Calls the onChange callback with the new value.

---

FUNCTION handleBlur(e)
  Runs validation on the current value.
  Sets error message state if validation fails.

---

FUNCTION TextInput(props) -> ReactNode                                    EXPORT
  Renders a labeled input field.
  Shows a validation error message below the field when invalid.
  Supports both controlled (value prop) and uncontrolled usage.
